---
const problems = [
  {
    number: "01",
    text: "You ask Claude a question. It gives the same answer it gives everyone. It doesn't know your clients, your projects, or how you think.",
  },
  {
    number: "02",
    text: "You tried building a system yourself. It took a weekend, worked for two weeks, then fell apart when your projects changed.",
  },
  {
    number: "03",
    text: "Every session starts from zero. Your AI has no memory of what you built last month, who you talked to, or what you decided.",
  },
];
---

<section class="py-24 px-4">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-zinc-100 text-center mb-16">
      Generic AI is worse than no AI.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {problems.map((p) => (
        <div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl p-6 relative">
          <div class="text-amber-400/30 font-display font-bold text-6xl absolute top-4 right-5 leading-none select-none pointer-events-none">{p.number}</div>
          <div class="text-amber-400 font-display font-bold text-2xl mb-4 relative z-10">{p.number}</div>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-base leading-relaxed relative z-10">{p.text}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-zinc-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      AI systems decay without maintenance.
      <span class="text-zinc-100 font-medium"> BrainKit is your maintenance contract.</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
